# HugeIcons Usage Guide

## Installation

```bash
yarn add @hugeicons/react
yarn add @hugeicons/core-free-icons
```

Packages:
- `@hugeicons/react` v1.1.3 - The main component
- `@hugeicons/core-free-icons` v3.0.0 - Free icon objects

> **Important**: This project uses the FREE version of HugeIcons. Always import icons from `@hugeicons/core-free-icons`, NOT from `@hugeicons/react`. The `@hugeicons/react` package only provides the `HugeiconsIcon` component, while the icon objects come from the free icons package.

## Documentation

- Official Docs: https://hugeicons.com/
